## Weekly Audit

After each Monday run, a technical reviewer confirms the following in the 
knitted HTML document:

- All three workflow sections completed without errors
- Token log shows no more than 2 source failures
- No single source call exceeded 90 seconds
- Total run cost is within the expected threshold
- The PDF brief was created and distributed successfully

